				>
					Book a call
				</a>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 sm:py-16 lg:py-24 pt-20 sm:pt-24 lg:pt-32">
				<div class="text-center motion-safe:animate-[rise_0.8s_ease-out]">
					<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-500 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-400">
						Technical video studio
					</span>
					<h1 class="mt-5 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl dark:text-white">
						Turn technical knowledge into developer-ready video.
					</h1>
					<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-gray-500 md:text-lg lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
