							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
								<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary-600"></span>
								Make video a larger part of your enablement strategy.
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
								<span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary-600"></span>
								Repurpose existing docs and demos for social clips.
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3">
