							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Video strategy and series planning</h3>
							<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
								Clarify the narrative, outline the series, and map content to product goals.
							</p>
						</article>
						<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Product demos that build confidence</h3>
							<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
								Hands-on walkthroughs that make complex workflows easy to adopt.
							</p>
						</article>
						<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Documentation to video pipelines</h3>
							<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
								Reuse existing docs, demos, and blog posts to speed up production.
							</p>
						</article>
						<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Fast, collaborative delivery</h3>
							<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
