						<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
							High-impact showcase reels and looping demos that explain your product at a glance.
						</p>
					</article>
					<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Short-form clips and social cutdowns</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
