						</p>
					</article>
					<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-800">
						<h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Narrative scripting and storyboards</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
							Translate technical detail into tight scripts and clean, confident delivery.
						</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900" id="my-work">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-12">
				<div class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-2xl text-center">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Recent work</p>
					<h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">My Work</h2>
					<p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
